Hello,

&gt; Can I configure the rules to crawl the entire site, but only mirror files that end with the PDF extension?

Yes, I believe so. You want to remove your special PDF decide rule from the scope section, then add it into your writer-processor. All of this can be done in the Submodules tab of the web ui.

Noah


